# Definition of Done Checklist

- "Security: inputs validated, secrets safe, no widened SQL permissions"
- "Architecture: logic in services, repositories; controllers thin"
- "Performance: DB pooled; limits/timeouts in place; no N+1 patterns introduced"
- "Style: lint/format pass; files and functions within size limits"
- "Tests: added/updated; CI green"
- "Docs: README or inline docs updated"
